    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make a finger gun and shoot a powerful chakra bullet. Make a ranged ninjutsu attack against a creature. On a hit you deal 3d6+2 Force damage. This bullet ricochets off the original target and to a different one. On a hit, select another creature within range, comparing the original attack roll vs the new target's AC. On a hit you deal the same rolled damage to the second target. If this jutsu would kill a target, you can choose to just knock them out.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d6+1. When casted at B-rank you may chain up to 3 targets. At S-rank this becomes 4 targets.</p>",
